				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/Ai-Nh%E1%BB%8B-Th%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%BA/poem-nHHf8iIeresXmdhEV-ABLA">Ai Nhị Thế phú - 哀二世賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/B%E1%BB%91c-c%C6%B0/poem-DaKKEOHDX-9jVox52Khj3Q">Bốc cư - 卜居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-iHGgucL9iiPjBtgwuopHKw">Cảm ngộ kỳ 10 - 感遇其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-Ng%C3%B4-Vi%E1%BB%87t-xu%C3%A2n-thu/poem-kQt8CA9is13pEsuRD-ZGzg">Độc “Ngô Việt xuân thu” - 讀吳越春秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/author-SWshGEoAx645s4epx95yPA">Quán Hưu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%A0n-bi/poem-aUyDGdFMte6NkDc2IR5eWA">Hàn bi - 韓碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ngh%E1%BB%87-T%C3%B4ng/H%E1%BA%A1nh-Gia-H%C6%B0ng-tr%E1%BA%A5n-k%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Cung-Tuy%C3%AAn-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-bFIIE8KRVUHmeA1Y4Tntjw">Hạnh Gia Hưng trấn ký đệ Cung Tuyên Vương - 幸嘉興鎮寄弟恭宣王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ngh%E1%BB%87-T%C3%B4ng/author-juCJQZYdn_Zgp256dfTydA">Trần Nghệ Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/Ly-tao/poem-kvKLhIt8jjW5-ExLsxl1UQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.